                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "0S5B0v4PS5xw3Uz1",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Accessorized",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The mannequin wears accessories (typically three) that it can Draw as a free action and use as thrown weapons. The type of damage varies by the accessory, such as slashing damage for a wide-brimmed hat, piercing for a stiletto-heeled shoe, or bludgeoning for a handbag.</p>"
                },
